                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9242" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-2310</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">733 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从品类品牌化到品牌品类化：水星家纺被芯业务深耕之旅</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From Category Branding to Brand Categorization: A Journey of Delving Deep in Quilt Business by Shanghai Shuixing Home Textile Stock Co., Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">侯仕军，王振源，丁哲琪，朱可欣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华东师范大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海水星家用纺织品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">纺织工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">19 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">业务战略；品牌战略；品类品牌化；品牌品类化；水星家纺</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Business Strategy; Brand Strategy; Category Branding; Brand Categorization; Shanghai Shuixing Home Textile Stock Co., Ltd.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了水星家纺深耕被芯品类、塑造被芯品牌并开发新品类、成长为国内被芯品类领军企业的历程。2019年底开始，水星家纺重温初心，综合历史渊源、现实市场和品类属性等因素，谋划重点发展被芯品类。2020年开始，水星家纺发力被芯业务，推出“好被芯 选水星”品牌战略，聚焦水星品牌建设，增强水星品牌优势，深入消费者心智。2021年以来，水星家纺依托被芯品类品牌优势，实施并延续“大单品策略”，强化功能性被芯核心品类优势、带动全品类发展。为此，水星家纺深入挖掘细分市场，开展产品创新，优化产品结构、并实现被芯品类快速发展。本案例旨在引导学习者学习品类品牌化和品牌品类化等相关理论，为家纺等行业企业业务品牌战略转变提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This study delineates the trajectory of Shanghai Shuixing Home Textile Stock Co., Ltd.’s immersive delve into the quilt category, its branding initiatives, and its ascension to a preeminent domestic enterprise. Commencing towards the close of 2019, the company rekindled its foundational resolve to concentrate on the advancement of the quilt category, informed by historical provenance, prevailing market dynamics, and categorical nuances. From 2020 onwards, the firm has been laser-focused on its quilt business, debuting the brand strategy &quot;Good Quilt Core from Mercury&quot;, with an emphasis on Mercury brand development, leveraging brand strengths, and embedding brand consciousness in the consumer psyche. Since 2021, Shanghai Shuixing Home Textile Stock Co., Ltd. has harnessed the brand equity within the quilt segment, systematically executing the &quot;Major Item Strategy&quot;, reinforcing the competitive edges of functional quilt categories, and propelling the expansion of the entire product spectrum. To this end, the company has penetrated niche markets, pioneered product innovation, refined product mix, and achieved exponential growth within the quilt segment. This case aims to guide learners in studying the theories related to category branding and brand categorization, providing references for the strategy transition of business brands in industries such as home textiles.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》、《市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业战略转变与企业业务增长战略；品类品牌化（品牌定位、品牌架构及其整合营销传播）；品牌品类化（品牌延伸/产品线延伸和新产品开发）</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-02</td>
                            </tr>
